1
00:00:00,060 --> 00:00:05,100
♪ Inside the state a city is built ♪

2
00:00:05,100 --> 00:00:10,220
♪ Where a benevolent emperor resides ♪

3
00:00:10,220 --> 00:00:15,380
♪ Court officials are brave and able ♪

4
00:00:15,380 --> 00:00:22,780
♪ The empress is fair ♪

5
00:00:25,620 --> 00:00:30,740
♪ Princes died too young to ascend the throne ♪

6
00:00:30,740 --> 00:00:35,620
♪ Princesses are spoiled and fragile ♪

7
00:00:35,860 --> 00:00:40,300
♪ Commoners are also the emperor’s children ♪

8
00:00:40,860 --> 00:00:49,660
♪ All are living peacefully ♪

9
00:00:49,980 --> 00:00:54,300
♪ Wish I could live a day for myself ♪

10
00:00:55,020 --> 00:00:59,420
♪ Follow my heart and ethics without distractions ♪

11
00:01:00,740 --> 00:01:03,420
♪ To be a good husband ♪

12
00:01:03,420 --> 00:01:06,020
♪ To be a caring father ♪

13
00:01:06,500 --> 00:01:10,140
♪ We were close when we first met ♪

14
00:01:10,500 --> 00:01:14,740
♪ I hope I can control my desires ♪

15
00:01:15,580 --> 00:01:20,100
♪ To be a worriless emperor and father ♪

16
00:01:21,140 --> 00:01:23,900
♪ Prudence tops all virtues ♪

17
00:01:23,900 --> 00:01:26,500
♪ People build the state ♪

18
00:01:26,780 --> 00:01:30,020
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
= Episode 64 =

20
00:01:38,300 --> 00:01:39,620
Huirou is very stubborn.

21
00:01:41,900 --> 00:01:43,460
She didn’t like Li Wei.

22
00:01:44,820 --> 00:01:45,940
After she was married into the Li family,

23
00:01:46,660 --> 00:01:47,860
she had to live

24
00:01:47,860 --> 00:01:49,140
in a strange place

25
00:01:49,340 --> 00:01:50,740
with a man she didn’t like.

26
00:01:51,220 --> 00:01:52,540
She must be very painful.

27
00:02:00,540 --> 00:02:01,540
Very painful.

28
00:02:05,820 --> 00:02:07,540
Huirou lives a painful life.

29
00:02:23,460 --> 00:02:24,260
Your Majesty,

30
00:02:26,780 --> 00:02:27,900
you should have a rest.

31
00:02:29,740 --> 00:02:32,620
I’m sure Li Wei will come tomorrow.

32
00:02:34,620 --> 00:02:35,580
I think

33
00:02:36,380 --> 00:02:37,620
the priority is

34
00:02:38,340 --> 00:02:39,980
to not to worsen the situation,

35
00:02:41,580 --> 00:02:43,020
so that censors won’t notice it.

36
00:03:08,740 --> 00:03:10,180
I hope so.

37
00:03:27,100 --> 00:03:30,020
I’ve failed in my duty.

38
00:03:31,700 --> 00:03:32,700
I’m unforgivable.

39
00:03:33,780 --> 00:03:35,020
Please punish me.

40
00:03:38,220 --> 00:03:38,940
Rise.

41
00:03:38,940 --> 00:03:39,820
I dare not!

42
00:03:41,420 --> 00:03:42,140
I...

43
00:03:44,660 --> 00:03:45,900
I’m unforgivable.

44
00:03:47,340 --> 00:03:48,780
Please punish me.

45
00:03:55,620 --> 00:03:57,060
Punish you for what?

46
00:03:59,180 --> 00:04:01,260
It’s common for couples to quarrel with each other.

47
00:04:02,380 --> 00:04:04,740
It’s just that you shouldn’t beat her.

48
00:04:06,020 --> 00:04:06,660
She...

49
00:04:08,340 --> 00:04:10,860
She’s a girl anyway, right?

50
00:04:17,900 --> 00:04:20,260
I’m guilty! I’m guilty!

51
00:04:22,620 --> 00:04:23,660
I’m a fool!

52
00:04:24,220 --> 00:04:26,340
I’m guilty! I’m a fool!

53
00:04:28,140 --> 00:04:29,100
= Hall of Happiness and Tranquility =
I’m a fool!

54
00:04:32,220 --> 00:04:33,020
I...

55
00:04:33,940 --> 00:04:34,740
You may rise.

56
00:04:37,460 --> 00:04:38,420
Let’s...

57
00:04:39,860 --> 00:04:41,220
Let’s talk about this later.

58
00:04:42,980 --> 00:04:43,900
You may go back now.

59
00:04:45,140 --> 00:04:46,580
Huirou doesn’t feel comfortable.

60
00:04:47,780 --> 00:04:49,100
I’ll have her stay in the palace

61
00:04:49,260 --> 00:04:50,580
for some days.

62
00:04:57,940 --> 00:04:58,660
Huirou...

63
00:05:01,140 --> 00:05:03,740
Will she...

64
00:05:04,700 --> 00:05:05,980
Will she forgive me?

65
00:05:09,220 --> 00:05:10,260
How about you?

66
00:05:12,260 --> 00:05:13,580
Will you blame Huirou?

67
00:05:30,724 --> 00:05:32,140
Of course not.

68
00:05:33,660 --> 00:05:34,700
I like her.

69
00:05:36,940 --> 00:05:38,780
Your Majesty, you know

70
00:05:39,820 --> 00:05:41,220
I like her since childhood.

71
00:05:44,620 --> 00:05:46,300
But there’s no way I can

72
00:05:48,020 --> 00:05:49,700
change my appearance to the way Huirou likes,

73
00:05:51,900 --> 00:05:53,660
like the appearance of Mr. Liang.

74
00:05:55,900 --> 00:05:58,460
Huirou likes to spend time with Mr. Liang,

75
00:05:58,860 --> 00:06:02,460
reading, painting,

76
00:06:03,457 --> 00:06:04,580
and writing with him.

77
00:06:06,900 --> 00:06:08,180
My paintings

78
00:06:08,460 --> 00:06:09,380
and handwriting

79
00:06:10,260 --> 00:06:11,700
are better than Mr. Liang’s.

80
00:06:13,860 --> 00:06:15,260
I thought Huirou would like me

81
00:06:16,300 --> 00:06:17,460
and thus want to spend more time with me

82
00:06:18,300 --> 00:06:19,740
after she saw my works.

83
00:06:23,380 --> 00:06:26,100
But in fact, Huirou

84
00:06:27,860 --> 00:06:29,820
just wants to be with Mr. Liang.

85
00:06:32,460 --> 00:06:33,660
She’s willing to do anything with him.

86
00:06:36,340 --> 00:06:37,300
She doesn’t

87
00:06:39,260 --> 00:06:43,580
really like to paint or write.

88
00:07:08,180 --> 00:07:08,980
Your Majesty.

89
00:07:18,580 --> 00:07:19,700
What does it say?

90
00:07:22,420 --> 00:07:24,940
Princess knocked on the palace gate at night.

91
00:07:25,500 --> 00:07:28,740
The gatekeeper passed on the message right away.

92
00:07:28,940 --> 00:07:32,060
The gate was opened and she went in the palace.

93
00:07:40,180 --> 00:07:41,100
Your Majesty.

94
00:07:42,660 --> 00:07:44,620
Where is Huirou? How is she?

95
00:07:46,020 --> 00:07:47,340
She’s still having a fever.

96
00:07:48,140 --> 00:07:49,900
She took some medicine after lunch.

97
00:07:50,580 --> 00:07:51,700
Now she’s still sleeping.

98
00:08:16,780 --> 00:08:17,620
Your Majesty,

99
00:08:19,653 --> 00:08:21,137
did Li Wei

100
00:08:22,020 --> 00:08:23,260
say anything to you?

101
00:08:26,100 --> 00:08:27,620
He only pleaded guilty.

102
00:08:29,460 --> 00:08:30,940
He’s a kind young man.

103
00:08:31,260 --> 00:08:32,380
He wouldn’t say anything.

104
00:08:38,460 --> 00:08:39,260
Huaiji,

105
00:08:39,740 --> 00:08:40,660
you’re here.

106
00:08:53,740 --> 00:08:55,060
Read it to Princess.

107
00:09:12,860 --> 00:09:14,420
According to Rites of the Zhou Dynasty,

108
00:09:15,020 --> 00:09:16,980
gatekeepers are responsible for

109
00:09:17,700 --> 00:09:18,900
opening and closing the gates

110
00:09:19,900 --> 00:09:21,460
of the imperial palace

111
00:09:22,140 --> 00:09:23,260
and exercising strict entry-exit control

112
00:09:24,100 --> 00:09:26,900
to strengthen palace defense.

113
00:09:27,500 --> 00:09:28,380
Are they...

114
00:09:29,420 --> 00:09:31,060
Are they impeaching Princess?

115
00:09:33,020 --> 00:09:33,900
Not yet.

116
00:09:35,420 --> 00:09:38,500
But they cited some examples in the history.

117
00:09:40,660 --> 00:09:44,060
Emperor Guangwu of Han returned at night.

118
00:09:44,300 --> 00:09:47,580
Zhi Yun refused to open the Upper East Gate.

119
00:09:48,780 --> 00:09:51,420
So he went in through the Middle East Gate.

120
00:09:51,620 --> 00:09:53,540
The next day, he rewarded Zhi Yun,

121
00:09:53,580 --> 00:09:55,260
and demoted the captain of the Middle East Gate.

122
00:09:56,100 --> 00:09:58,580
Cao Zhi, the son of Emperor Wu of Wei, Cao Cao,

123
00:09:58,740 --> 00:10:00,580
opened the Sima Gate privately and went out.

124
00:10:00,580 --> 00:10:01,540
Cao Cao was furious

125
00:10:02,500 --> 00:10:03,260
and killed

126
00:10:03,260 --> 00:10:05,060
the Prefect of the Majors for Official Carriages.

127
00:10:09,020 --> 00:10:11,660
What... What does this mean?

128
00:10:14,300 --> 00:10:16,860
Huaiji, read the last paragraph.

129
00:10:23,300 --> 00:10:24,100
However,

130
00:10:24,940 --> 00:10:27,940
the gatekeepers opened the gate

131
00:10:28,540 --> 00:10:31,620
and let Princess enter the palace

132
00:10:32,340 --> 00:10:34,660
without confirming if it’s really the princess.

133
00:10:36,020 --> 00:10:37,540
All the gatekeepers of the gate

134
00:10:37,740 --> 00:10:39,780
where she went through to the imperial palace

135
00:10:40,060 --> 00:10:42,540
should be sent to Kaifeng Municipal Government.

136
00:10:45,140 --> 00:10:46,420
I knocked on the gate.

137
00:10:46,780 --> 00:10:47,660
If the censors are angry,

138
00:10:47,820 --> 00:10:49,060
they can abuse me directly.

139
00:10:49,660 --> 00:10:51,380
Why try to condemn the gatekeepers?

140
00:10:53,340 --> 00:10:55,460
You think they don’t want to abuse you?

141
00:10:57,100 --> 00:10:58,340
They even want to

142
00:10:58,340 --> 00:10:59,420
abuse me.

143
00:11:00,780 --> 00:11:02,380
If I didn’t give the order,

144
00:11:02,380 --> 00:11:03,700
who’d dare to open the gate at night?

145
00:11:07,740 --> 00:11:09,540
The censors have some misgivings

146
00:11:10,100 --> 00:11:11,660
about condemning us directly,

147
00:11:11,860 --> 00:11:13,500
so they started with the gatekeepers.

148
00:11:14,660 --> 00:11:15,820
If I punish those gatekeepers,

149
00:11:16,540 --> 00:11:17,460
it’d be a real slap

150
00:11:17,460 --> 00:11:18,580
on my face.

151
00:11:21,140 --> 00:11:22,260
Will you

152
00:11:22,260 --> 00:11:23,500
punish them?

153
00:11:23,580 --> 00:11:24,460
I won’t.

154
00:11:25,380 --> 00:11:27,140
They were just following my order.

155
00:11:27,740 --> 00:11:29,700
I can’t let them take responsibility for it.

156
00:11:31,940 --> 00:11:34,740
Father, Huaiji...

157
00:11:43,180 --> 00:11:44,540
Now you’ve seen Huaiji,

158
00:11:45,620 --> 00:11:47,140
you can feel at ease.

159
00:11:48,140 --> 00:11:49,060
I

160
00:11:50,140 --> 00:11:51,620
didn’t let him

161
00:11:51,660 --> 00:11:53,020
take full responsibility for your mistake.

162
00:11:54,020 --> 00:11:55,860
Father, he didn’t do anything wrong.

163
00:11:56,060 --> 00:11:56,860
It was

164
00:11:56,940 --> 00:11:58,220
all my fault.

165
00:11:59,740 --> 00:12:01,020
If he hadn’t been at fault,

166
00:12:02,140 --> 00:12:04,060
nothing would have happened.

167
00:12:07,820 --> 00:12:09,140
Huaiji will serve me for a few days.

168
00:12:10,940 --> 00:12:12,340
You should get some good rest.

169
00:12:13,820 --> 00:12:15,500
I will cope with the censors.

170
00:12:15,980 --> 00:12:17,540
And I won’t punish those gatekeepers.

171
00:12:19,660 --> 00:12:20,820
The Empress will go

172
00:12:21,620 --> 00:12:23,260
apologize to Mrs. Yang today.

173
00:12:24,380 --> 00:12:25,460
Apologize to her?

174
00:12:26,340 --> 00:12:27,740
Why should we apologize to her?

175
00:12:36,420 --> 00:12:37,980
Because you,

176
00:12:39,620 --> 00:12:40,540
as Li Wei’s wife,

177
00:12:41,820 --> 00:12:44,180
did intimate things with another man.

178
00:12:45,140 --> 00:12:47,020
When caught and scolded by your mother-in-law,

179
00:12:48,500 --> 00:12:49,900
you beat her.

180
00:12:51,780 --> 00:12:54,180
Father, you know

181
00:12:54,620 --> 00:12:55,580
how vulgar

182
00:12:55,580 --> 00:12:56,980
and unreasonable

183
00:12:57,060 --> 00:12:58,220
Li Wei’s mother is.

184
00:12:58,220 --> 00:13:00,180
It’s fine that you dislike her.

185
00:13:01,060 --> 00:13:01,860
After she drugged you,

186
00:13:01,860 --> 00:13:03,340
you could choose to tell me

187
00:13:03,340 --> 00:13:04,420
or scold her.

188
00:13:06,140 --> 00:13:07,340
But instead,

189
00:13:07,700 --> 00:13:09,420
you acted frivolously with a eunuch,

190
00:13:09,820 --> 00:13:11,060
and then beat her.

191
00:13:13,780 --> 00:13:15,500
You think we shouldn’t apologize

192
00:13:15,500 --> 00:13:16,700
for not educating you well?

193
00:13:17,100 --> 00:13:18,860
Do you expect us to use our power

194
00:13:19,060 --> 00:13:20,340
to relieve your anger?

195
00:14:04,660 --> 00:14:05,500
Your Highness.

196
00:14:19,220 --> 00:14:20,220
What did Mrs. Yang say?

197
00:14:21,700 --> 00:14:22,380
Sit.

198
00:14:27,964 --> 00:14:29,380
Mrs. Yang cried and told me

199
00:14:29,700 --> 00:14:30,980
how Princess beat her.

200
00:14:31,911 --> 00:14:33,060
Fortunately, she’s not badly injured.

201
00:14:33,786 --> 00:14:34,820
I comforted her

202
00:14:35,460 --> 00:14:37,700
and implied that if the situation blows up,

203
00:14:38,180 --> 00:14:40,060
both Li Wei and Princess

204
00:14:40,300 --> 00:14:42,420
will become the talk of the town.

205
00:14:43,700 --> 00:14:45,740
Li Wei beat Princess.

206
00:14:45,980 --> 00:14:47,140
He’ll be accused of

207
00:14:47,220 --> 00:14:48,660
disrespecting you.

208
00:14:50,020 --> 00:14:52,140
Mrs. Yang promised me

209
00:14:52,580 --> 00:14:54,700
she’ll never mention it to others.

210
00:15:02,900 --> 00:15:04,020
Serve the dishes.

211
00:15:07,820 --> 00:15:09,380
You haven’t eaten yet?

212
00:15:11,940 --> 00:15:13,540
Did you enjoy your meal

213
00:15:13,940 --> 00:15:15,140
with Mrs. Yang?

214
00:15:26,462 --> 00:15:27,980
Mrs. Yang and Li Wei

215
00:15:28,780 --> 00:15:30,540
won’t tell it to others.

216
00:15:31,300 --> 00:15:33,460
But there are many servants

217
00:15:33,780 --> 00:15:34,820
in Princess’s Mansion.

218
00:15:36,100 --> 00:15:37,620
If Princess stays in the palace

219
00:15:37,940 --> 00:15:38,900
for too long,

220
00:15:40,500 --> 00:15:43,380
I’m afraid the censors will notice it.

221
00:15:44,700 --> 00:15:46,260
If they pursue this matter,

222
00:15:47,180 --> 00:15:49,020
it won’t do any good.

223
00:15:50,500 --> 00:15:51,900
I think Huirou should go back

224
00:15:53,180 --> 00:15:54,660
in a few days.

225
00:15:56,020 --> 00:15:58,500
She and Li Wei can still live separately.

226
00:15:59,100 --> 00:16:01,300
And we can let Li Wei take a concubine.

227
00:16:02,380 --> 00:16:03,620
Maybe after some time,

228
00:16:04,180 --> 00:16:06,380
Huirou will realize how much Li Wei loves her.

229
00:16:07,380 --> 00:16:08,613
It’d be great

230
00:16:08,613 --> 00:16:09,475
if they can move a step further

231
00:16:09,480 --> 00:16:10,580
in their relationship.

232
00:16:12,700 --> 00:16:13,620
If not,

233
00:16:15,260 --> 00:16:16,660
we can say Princess is sick,

234
00:16:17,620 --> 00:16:19,420
and get her back to the palace.

235
00:16:29,020 --> 00:16:30,380
Your mother passed away.

236
00:16:30,940 --> 00:16:32,380
It’s only natural that

237
00:16:33,100 --> 00:16:34,220
you want to resign to mourn her.

238
00:16:36,020 --> 00:16:38,180
= Fu Bi, courtesy name Yanguo =
However, traditionally,

239
00:16:39,140 --> 00:16:41,060
ministers who resign to mourn will be reappointed.

240
00:16:41,860 --> 00:16:43,060
You can still be the minister.

241
00:16:44,100 --> 00:16:45,620
Normally, ministers will be reappointed

242
00:16:46,340 --> 00:16:47,260
because it’s war time,

243
00:16:47,820 --> 00:16:49,700
or they’re extraordinarily capable.

244
00:16:50,900 --> 00:16:52,140
Now it’s a peaceful era,

245
00:16:52,380 --> 00:16:53,500
and I don’t have special talents,

246
00:16:53,700 --> 00:16:54,900
so there’s no reason to reappoint me.

247
00:16:56,220 --> 00:16:58,620
Please approve of my resignation.

248
00:17:07,700 --> 00:17:08,700
But before leaving,

249
00:17:09,660 --> 00:17:11,300
I have something to say.

250
00:17:16,740 --> 00:17:17,540
Go ahead.

251
00:17:23,220 --> 00:17:24,580
Your Majesty, you’re eager to have a son.

252
00:17:25,620 --> 00:17:26,580
All the madams

253
00:17:26,820 --> 00:17:28,460
want to be favored by you.

254
00:17:29,500 --> 00:17:30,900
Now they know you want a son,

255
00:17:31,820 --> 00:17:33,340
of course they’ll do their best

256
00:17:33,340 --> 00:17:34,420
to serve you.

257
00:17:36,060 --> 00:17:37,060
You’re kind.

258
00:17:37,580 --> 00:17:38,980
You don’t want to be partial.

259
00:17:41,220 --> 00:17:41,980
However,

260
00:17:42,620 --> 00:17:44,740
it’ll do harm to your body.

261
00:17:46,820 --> 00:17:47,500
I heard that

262
00:17:47,900 --> 00:17:48,820
four princesses were born

263
00:17:49,020 --> 00:17:50,740
in less than a year.

264
00:17:51,420 --> 00:17:54,460
I really worry about your health.

265
00:17:55,980 --> 00:17:57,540
You’re getting on in years,

266
00:17:58,300 --> 00:17:59,500
but you haven’t chosen the Crown Prince.

267
00:17:59,860 --> 00:18:01,740
I worry about our country even more.

268
00:18:02,260 --> 00:18:03,100
Madam Miao

269
00:18:04,140 --> 00:18:05,580
gave birth to Prince Yue.

270
00:18:08,380 --> 00:18:09,500
He was talented,

271
00:18:10,900 --> 00:18:11,780
and you liked him very much.

272
00:18:13,940 --> 00:18:15,380
If Heaven had been on your side,

273
00:18:16,420 --> 00:18:17,940
Prince Yue would’ve grown into an adult

274
00:18:18,420 --> 00:18:19,540
and shared your burdens now.

275
00:18:21,060 --> 00:18:23,500
Father, there’s an insect in mother’s painting.

276
00:18:23,620 --> 00:18:24,980
Mother said it’s not a grasshopper

277
00:18:24,980 --> 00:18:25,980
or a cricket,

278
00:18:25,980 --> 00:18:28,740
but a flying cricket with the most beautiful voice.

279
00:18:54,860 --> 00:18:55,700
I...

280
00:18:57,500 --> 00:18:58,780
I’m not talented,

281
00:19:01,100 --> 00:19:01,860
and I’m dull.

282
00:19:03,300 --> 00:19:05,340
I haven’t made any contributions to our country.

283
00:19:08,820 --> 00:19:10,180
I can only work wholeheartedly

284
00:19:10,580 --> 00:19:13,420
to repay your gracious kindness.

285
00:19:15,100 --> 00:19:16,420
I’m speaking

286
00:19:17,300 --> 00:19:20,020
from the bottom of my heart.

287
00:19:20,820 --> 00:19:24,620
My words are sharp and aggressive,

288
00:19:25,540 --> 00:19:26,500
and might have offended you.

289
00:19:28,020 --> 00:19:29,820
If you can follow my advice

290
00:19:30,380 --> 00:19:31,300
and select a successor,

291
00:19:33,180 --> 00:19:34,940
I’m willing to die

292
00:19:37,540 --> 00:19:38,700
even if you grant me death.

293
00:19:50,900 --> 00:19:52,660
You’re doing this for the sake of the state.

294
00:19:55,140 --> 00:19:56,700
How could I blame you?

295
00:19:57,860 --> 00:19:58,620
However,

296
00:20:01,500 --> 00:20:03,700
I also have a question.

297
00:20:07,220 --> 00:20:10,700
I’m not sure if I should ask you.

298
00:20:12,300 --> 00:20:13,460
Ruolan died early.

299
00:20:15,380 --> 00:20:17,740
Then you married Ruozhu off to Feng Jing.

300
00:20:19,020 --> 00:20:21,260
So that peerless principal graduate

301
00:20:21,260 --> 00:20:23,020
would still be your son-in-law.

302
00:20:25,580 --> 00:20:27,580
Ruolan was bed-ridden for nearly a year.

303
00:20:28,420 --> 00:20:30,340
I wonder, when Ruolan was critically ill,

304
00:20:30,380 --> 00:20:31,820
did you already promise Ruozhu

305
00:20:32,220 --> 00:20:33,540
you’ll marry her off

306
00:20:34,580 --> 00:20:35,500
to his brother-in-law

307
00:20:36,700 --> 00:20:37,820
if Ruolan can’t make it?

308
00:21:01,500 --> 00:21:03,660
What if Ruolan gets better?

309
00:21:05,100 --> 00:21:07,580
How will she get along with Ruozhu

310
00:21:08,300 --> 00:21:10,340
if she learns about your arrangement?

311
00:21:12,580 --> 00:21:15,540
How should Ruozhu

312
00:21:16,180 --> 00:21:17,780
deal with the situation

313
00:21:18,540 --> 00:21:20,220
if she sees Feng Jing as her husband

314
00:21:21,260 --> 00:21:22,780
but Ruolan gets better later?

315
00:21:37,140 --> 00:21:39,260
You’re afraid that if something happens to me,

316
00:21:40,180 --> 00:21:41,900
our country will fall into chaos.

317
00:21:44,900 --> 00:21:46,140
I can designate

318
00:21:46,220 --> 00:21:48,780
my foster son as the Crown Prince today.

319
00:21:49,020 --> 00:21:50,500
It’d prove to be a wise decision

320
00:21:50,500 --> 00:21:51,780
if I died tomorrow.

321
00:21:53,340 --> 00:21:55,300
But if I live for another few years,

322
00:21:56,300 --> 00:21:57,860
and even manage to have a son,

323
00:21:59,020 --> 00:21:59,660
tell me,

324
00:22:01,180 --> 00:22:03,980
how should my birth son and foster son

325
00:22:04,860 --> 00:22:07,340
get along with each other after I die?

326
00:22:07,580 --> 00:22:08,780
They’ll turn against each other

327
00:22:09,020 --> 00:22:10,460
no matter who ascends the throne.

328
00:22:14,300 --> 00:22:15,260
Our country

329
00:22:16,980 --> 00:22:19,100
will still fall into chaos.

330
00:22:21,140 --> 00:22:25,140
= Fu Bi died in 1083 A.D.,
with a posthumous title Wenzhong =

331
00:22:25,140 --> 00:22:28,420
= One of the 24 meritorious officials
(paintings hung in Zhaoxun Pavilion) =

332
00:22:42,770 --> 00:22:43,570
Your Majesty,

333
00:22:44,090 --> 00:22:45,130
Prince Consort

334
00:22:45,130 --> 00:22:46,330
has been here for quite a while.

335
00:22:46,770 --> 00:22:48,330
He stood at the gate in the beginning.

336
00:22:48,810 --> 00:22:51,130
Then the Empress came

337
00:22:51,570 --> 00:22:54,010
and said she’ll try and persuade Princess.

338
00:23:01,850 --> 00:23:02,690
Let him go.

339
00:23:04,690 --> 00:23:05,570
Let him go.

340
00:23:07,450 --> 00:23:08,370
Let him go.

341
00:23:11,810 --> 00:23:13,210
I don’t want to see him.

342
00:23:14,530 --> 00:23:16,010
I don’t want to see him.

343
00:23:19,097 --> 00:23:19,850
Huirou,

344
00:23:21,090 --> 00:23:22,610
Li Wei has admitted his mistake.

345
00:23:24,130 --> 00:23:25,410
He’s promised that

346
00:23:25,410 --> 00:23:26,250
in the future...

347
00:23:26,250 --> 00:23:26,850
No!

348
00:23:28,530 --> 00:23:29,490
There’s no future for us.

349
00:23:31,666 --> 00:23:32,890
There’s no future for us.

350
00:23:35,330 --> 00:23:36,330
No future for us.

351
00:23:43,090 --> 00:23:43,810
Huirou!

352
00:23:44,090 --> 00:23:45,250
Huirou! Huirou!

353
00:23:46,890 --> 00:23:48,690
Huirou, what are you doing?

354
00:24:02,770 --> 00:24:05,050
Mother, I don’t want to go back.

355
00:24:07,250 --> 00:24:08,490
I don’t want to go back.

356
00:24:08,890 --> 00:24:10,290
I don’t want to go back.

357
00:24:12,010 --> 00:24:12,930
Let him go.

358
00:24:13,650 --> 00:24:14,690
Please beg father.

359
00:24:15,450 --> 00:24:16,450
I’m not going back.

360
00:24:16,850 --> 00:24:18,050
I won’t let you go back.

361
00:24:18,170 --> 00:24:20,090
I would rather die than go back.

362
00:24:21,770 --> 00:24:22,970
Alright. Alright.

363
00:24:23,090 --> 00:24:24,210
I won’t let you go back.

364
00:24:24,497 --> 00:24:25,930
I won’t let you go back.

365
00:24:42,050 --> 00:24:42,810
Your Majesty.

366
00:24:44,370 --> 00:24:46,290
No! No!

367
00:24:47,930 --> 00:24:50,610
Mother, please beg father for me.

368
00:24:51,570 --> 00:24:52,490
Please beg father

369
00:24:52,970 --> 00:24:54,410
not to send me to Li Wei.

370
00:24:54,730 --> 00:24:56,650
Don’t give me to the Li family as a gift.

371
00:24:56,650 --> 00:24:57,450
No!

372
00:24:57,450 --> 00:24:58,610
He won’t do this.

373
00:25:00,130 --> 00:25:01,130
He will.

374
00:25:01,730 --> 00:25:02,650
He will.

375
00:25:03,770 --> 00:25:05,170
He thinks Li Wei is a good person.

376
00:25:05,170 --> 00:25:07,370
He thinks the Li family is good.

377
00:25:07,890 --> 00:25:08,770
Mother!

378
00:25:09,250 --> 00:25:10,570
Mother, I’d rather die

379
00:25:10,570 --> 00:25:11,850
than go back there.

380
00:25:12,170 --> 00:25:13,250
Your Majesty, Your Highness,

381
00:25:13,610 --> 00:25:15,210
please don’t send Huirou away.

382
00:25:15,210 --> 00:25:15,930
Xinhe,

383
00:25:17,250 --> 00:25:18,810
I’ll explain this to you later.

384
00:25:26,250 --> 00:25:27,130
Your Majesty,

385
00:25:30,010 --> 00:25:31,370
the happiest moment in my life

386
00:25:32,290 --> 00:25:34,410
is when I watched Huirou

387
00:25:34,970 --> 00:25:37,130
teasing Zuixinglai with a cloth tiger.

388
00:25:39,130 --> 00:25:41,410
I wished our son can amount to something,

389
00:25:42,050 --> 00:25:43,690
and our daughter can marry a good husband.

390
00:25:45,850 --> 00:25:46,970
Now I just hope

391
00:25:46,970 --> 00:25:48,210
I can keep Huirou by my side safely.

392
00:25:49,450 --> 00:25:50,690
If you don’t agree,

393
00:25:52,130 --> 00:25:53,530
Huirou will end her life.

394
00:25:55,770 --> 00:25:56,890
Then I’ll meet Zuixinglai in heaven

395
00:25:58,130 --> 00:26:00,410
together with Huirou.

396
00:26:16,170 --> 00:26:18,930
Here are some paintings and calligraphy works.

397
00:26:19,570 --> 00:26:22,170
You can choose some

398
00:26:22,530 --> 00:26:24,730
Huirou might like.

399
00:26:27,730 --> 00:26:28,410
I...

400
00:26:31,090 --> 00:26:31,850
She...

401
00:26:34,130 --> 00:26:35,370
Be patient.

402
00:26:36,730 --> 00:26:39,730
You can go back to read some books

403
00:26:41,890 --> 00:26:42,730
and study some paintings.

404
00:26:45,050 --> 00:26:46,050
Don’t be so eager.

405
00:26:48,170 --> 00:26:48,930
Huirou...

406
00:27:18,570 --> 00:27:19,850
You can go back first.

407
00:27:21,610 --> 00:27:23,250
Huirou doesn’t feel well.

408
00:27:23,570 --> 00:27:25,170
Madam Miao wants to take care of her.

409
00:27:38,010 --> 00:27:40,050
If Huirou doesn’t want to see me,

410
00:27:41,050 --> 00:27:42,090
then I’ll stop bothering her.

411
00:27:44,930 --> 00:27:46,010
I’ll leave

412
00:27:46,570 --> 00:27:47,610
these paintings here.

413
00:27:48,610 --> 00:27:49,450
Huirou wouldn’t like

414
00:27:51,130 --> 00:27:52,210
the paintings I choose.

415
00:27:52,970 --> 00:27:53,690
Your Majesty,

416
00:27:57,450 --> 00:27:59,450
please let Mr. Liang do that for her.

417
00:28:31,610 --> 00:28:32,450
Xiao Ye’er,

418
00:28:32,810 --> 00:28:35,090
bring the osmanthus sugar

419
00:28:35,370 --> 00:28:36,250
and candied fruits

420
00:28:36,570 --> 00:28:37,970
Mr. Liang bought yesterday.

421
00:28:44,890 --> 00:28:45,650
Mother,

422
00:28:47,570 --> 00:28:49,050
I don’t want to go back there.

423
00:28:50,450 --> 00:28:52,170
Let me live in the palace forever,

424
00:28:54,050 --> 00:28:54,850
alright?

425
00:28:59,970 --> 00:29:01,290
I’ll think of a way.

426
00:29:03,970 --> 00:29:04,850
But,

427
00:29:05,730 --> 00:29:07,930
Her Highness asked me

428
00:29:09,010 --> 00:29:10,490
to go back first.

429
00:29:11,250 --> 00:29:13,410
But... But...

430
00:29:14,050 --> 00:29:16,170
I don’t want to see Li Wei and his mother.

431
00:29:18,650 --> 00:29:19,930
I’ll

432
00:29:21,170 --> 00:29:24,090
plead with your father and the empress.

433
00:29:24,090 --> 00:29:24,850
Madam,

434
00:29:25,570 --> 00:29:26,610
His Majesty sent Officer Ren here

435
00:29:26,610 --> 00:29:28,010
to check on Princess,

436
00:29:28,250 --> 00:29:30,690
and then pass on a message to Li Wei.

437
00:29:34,210 --> 00:29:34,970
Mother!

438
00:29:36,650 --> 00:29:37,450
It’s fine.

439
00:29:54,650 --> 00:29:56,050
Princess cried for a long time.

440
00:29:56,690 --> 00:29:57,970
She just felt a little better.

441
00:29:59,730 --> 00:30:01,770
We can’t mention Li Wei

442
00:30:01,770 --> 00:30:03,090
or the Li Family before her.

443
00:30:04,370 --> 00:30:05,730
Please tell this

444
00:30:06,650 --> 00:30:07,770
to His Majesty.

445
00:30:09,250 --> 00:30:10,530
The best choice for them

446
00:30:11,690 --> 00:30:12,970
is to divorce.

447
00:30:15,850 --> 00:30:17,370
You’re right.

448
00:30:18,570 --> 00:30:21,090
But His Majesty

449
00:30:21,250 --> 00:30:23,010
personally arranged this marriage.

450
00:30:24,370 --> 00:30:26,530
Li Wei is Empress Dowager Zhangyi’s nephew.

451
00:30:27,170 --> 00:30:30,930
All the officials approved of the marriage.

452
00:30:32,370 --> 00:30:34,210
If His Majesty grants a divorce,

453
00:30:34,730 --> 00:30:35,890
I’m afraid the censors

454
00:30:36,650 --> 00:30:37,810
will admonish him.

455
00:30:38,690 --> 00:30:39,970
They don’t have to divorce immediately.

456
00:30:41,210 --> 00:30:42,610
It’d be great if they can live separately

457
00:30:42,730 --> 00:30:44,010
for a year or so.

458
00:30:46,490 --> 00:30:47,450
But,

459
00:30:49,330 --> 00:30:50,770
His Majesty and Her Highness

460
00:30:51,690 --> 00:30:53,650
want Huirou to go back.

461
00:30:55,850 --> 00:30:57,970
And Li Wei constantly came to

462
00:30:58,530 --> 00:30:59,690
ask for Huirou’s forgiveness.

463
00:31:02,010 --> 00:31:03,970
Even if His Majesty concedes,

464
00:31:04,770 --> 00:31:05,970
I think Her Highness

465
00:31:07,530 --> 00:31:09,530
will come to send Huirou back in a few days.

466
00:31:11,890 --> 00:31:13,370
It’s not hard

467
00:31:13,370 --> 00:31:14,650
to let Princess and Prince Consort

468
00:31:14,930 --> 00:31:16,010
live separately for some time.

469
00:31:16,330 --> 00:31:18,290
If that’s really what you want,

470
00:31:18,290 --> 00:31:20,090
I’ll go talk with Prince Consort

471
00:31:20,650 --> 00:31:21,970
immediately

472
00:31:22,170 --> 00:31:24,210
and ask him to leave the Capital.

473
00:31:27,170 --> 00:31:28,930
You can persuade him to do that?

474
00:31:30,770 --> 00:31:33,850
You can wait for the good news.

475
00:31:39,010 --> 00:31:39,770
You know,

476
00:31:40,370 --> 00:31:41,970
we can’t let Her Highness know this.

477
00:32:01,100 --> 00:32:01,900
Your Majesty.

478
00:32:17,100 --> 00:32:17,860
Your Majesty.

479
00:32:18,260 --> 00:32:19,660
Please let me summon the physician.

480
00:32:22,340 --> 00:32:23,580
They’ll let me take the same medicine.

481
00:32:24,540 --> 00:32:25,500
It’s been so many years.

482
00:32:25,500 --> 00:32:26,780
I can write out a prescription myself.

483
00:32:27,780 --> 00:32:29,260
Plus, I don’t want them to nag me.

484
00:32:32,580 --> 00:32:33,380
Madam Miao.

485
00:32:45,820 --> 00:32:46,580
Your Majesty.

486
00:32:48,780 --> 00:32:49,900
Have you had dinner?

487
00:32:50,460 --> 00:32:51,300
How is Huirou?

488
00:32:55,660 --> 00:32:57,060
I heard that

489
00:32:58,380 --> 00:32:59,900
Li Wei submitted a proposal

490
00:33:00,740 --> 00:33:02,700
listing some of his mistakes

491
00:33:03,220 --> 00:33:04,380
and asked Your Majesty

492
00:33:04,940 --> 00:33:06,100
to let him leave the Capital.

493
00:33:07,020 --> 00:33:08,260
So I came to ask

494
00:33:08,980 --> 00:33:10,780
if you’ve approved of his request.

495
00:33:15,260 --> 00:33:17,660
I asked Officer Ren about this.

496
00:33:25,780 --> 00:33:27,140
Your Majesty asked me

497
00:33:28,140 --> 00:33:29,380
how Huirou is doing.

498
00:33:30,900 --> 00:33:32,340
I’ll just tell you the truth.

499
00:33:33,700 --> 00:33:35,860
She’d become so frightened

500
00:33:36,220 --> 00:33:37,500
when she hears Li Wei’s name.

501
00:33:38,500 --> 00:33:39,620
Last night,

502
00:33:39,860 --> 00:33:42,180
she woke up and said Li Wei came for her.

503
00:33:43,180 --> 00:33:44,380
I comforted her for quite a while.

504
00:33:44,780 --> 00:33:46,460
She cried so hard that she vomited.

505
00:33:47,140 --> 00:33:48,860
And she kept saying

506
00:33:49,060 --> 00:33:50,180
she doesn’t want to see Li Wei.

507
00:33:52,500 --> 00:33:53,340
Your Majesty,

508
00:33:55,140 --> 00:33:56,940
please approve of Li Wei’s request.

509
00:33:56,940 --> 00:33:58,980
Let him work in a different city for a year or so,

510
00:33:59,140 --> 00:34:00,580
so that both of them can calm down.

511
00:34:01,180 --> 00:34:01,980
Isn’t that good?

512
00:34:04,860 --> 00:34:06,740
But Li Wei didn’t do anything wrong.

513
00:34:07,940 --> 00:34:10,260
Huirou refused to share the same room with him,

514
00:34:11,060 --> 00:34:12,740
but he always treated her nicely.

515
00:34:13,660 --> 00:34:15,260
Mrs. Yang was having

516
00:34:15,260 --> 00:34:16,460
some issues with Huirou,

517
00:34:17,100 --> 00:34:18,420
but Li Wei never

518
00:34:18,420 --> 00:34:19,500
disrespected Huirou.

519
00:34:20,340 --> 00:34:22,500
Now Huirou

520
00:34:26,540 --> 00:34:28,140
blames Li Wei for everything.

521
00:34:28,140 --> 00:34:29,300
It’s not fair.

522
00:34:29,300 --> 00:34:30,460
Will you choose fairness

523
00:34:30,460 --> 00:34:31,700
over our daughter’s life?

524
00:34:42,860 --> 00:34:44,420
I’ve been with you for so many years.

525
00:34:45,100 --> 00:34:46,740
I haven’t made any contributions,

526
00:34:49,060 --> 00:34:50,253
but I never behaved

527
00:34:50,262 --> 00:34:51,260
improperly,

528
00:34:52,420 --> 00:34:54,260
and I never begged you to do anything.

529
00:34:56,060 --> 00:34:57,980
Now I beg you to

530
00:34:59,340 --> 00:35:00,900
approve of Li Wei’s request,

531
00:35:03,380 --> 00:35:04,940
and save our daughter’s life.

532
00:35:09,900 --> 00:35:11,100
If you think

533
00:35:11,100 --> 00:35:12,580
I’m interfering with politics,

534
00:35:14,060 --> 00:35:15,380
you can punish me severely.

535
00:35:17,980 --> 00:35:19,540
I only hope you can let Li Wei

536
00:35:19,860 --> 00:35:21,020
leave the Capital.

537
00:35:28,260 --> 00:35:29,380
I was the one

538
00:35:32,220 --> 00:35:33,500
that caused all this.

539
00:35:35,740 --> 00:35:37,260
Li Wei is innocent.

540
00:35:39,580 --> 00:35:40,380
Your Majesty,

541
00:35:41,940 --> 00:35:42,900
a few days ago,

542
00:35:43,580 --> 00:35:45,660
you ordered me to go to Princess’s Mansion

543
00:35:45,660 --> 00:35:46,660
to appease Prince Consort.

544
00:35:47,300 --> 00:35:48,900
Prince Consort was very scared.

545
00:35:49,780 --> 00:35:52,060
He repeatedly said he wants to leave the Capital.

546
00:35:53,020 --> 00:35:56,020
I know you are kind,

547
00:35:56,900 --> 00:35:58,900
and you don’t want to treat Prince Consort wrongly.

548
00:36:00,540 --> 00:36:02,780
But letting him leave the Capital

549
00:36:02,860 --> 00:36:04,340
is not necessarily treating him unfairly.

550
00:36:04,780 --> 00:36:07,860
You can send him to a good place

551
00:36:08,620 --> 00:36:10,140
and then comfort him privately.

552
00:36:10,940 --> 00:36:11,900
I think

553
00:36:12,500 --> 00:36:13,820
Prince Consort can live

554
00:36:14,860 --> 00:36:16,620
more freely than in the Capital.

555
00:36:23,300 --> 00:36:24,980
I’m such a dotard.

556
00:36:25,260 --> 00:36:27,660
I shouldn’t make comments on your decision.

557
00:36:27,940 --> 00:36:30,780
It’s just I feel very sad

558
00:36:32,940 --> 00:36:33,860
when I see Princess.

559
00:36:45,020 --> 00:36:45,900
Your Majesty,

560
00:36:48,020 --> 00:36:49,420
please approve of

561
00:36:50,380 --> 00:36:51,740
Li Wei’s request.

562
00:37:01,540 --> 00:37:02,580
I’m begging you.

563
00:37:03,860 --> 00:37:04,620
Brother!

564
00:37:15,820 --> 00:37:18,580
Today your father will make an announcement.

565
00:37:20,140 --> 00:37:21,420
Li Wei will be demoted

566
00:37:22,780 --> 00:37:24,020
and work in a different city

567
00:37:24,740 --> 00:37:25,740
because of his grave mistakes.

568
00:37:28,540 --> 00:37:29,340
Thus,

569
00:37:30,220 --> 00:37:32,340
you won’t see each other for one year or two.

570
00:37:33,820 --> 00:37:34,540
Really?

571
00:37:35,300 --> 00:37:36,260
Father agreed?

572
00:37:37,740 --> 00:37:38,700
Right.

573
00:37:41,060 --> 00:37:41,940
But your father thinks

574
00:37:43,380 --> 00:37:45,100
it’s unfair to Li Wei.

575
00:37:46,260 --> 00:37:47,260
Unfair to him?

576
00:37:47,940 --> 00:37:48,780
He beat me!

577
00:37:49,820 --> 00:37:50,660
Did father

578
00:37:50,660 --> 00:37:51,860
ever beat me?

579
00:37:53,260 --> 00:37:55,060
Mother, you know what?

580
00:37:55,420 --> 00:37:56,300
Every time I saw Li Wei’s mother,

581
00:37:56,300 --> 00:37:57,420
I became so angry

582
00:37:57,940 --> 00:37:59,300
that I couldn’t even breathe.

583
00:38:00,660 --> 00:38:01,980
She even drugged me later!

584
00:38:02,580 --> 00:38:04,020
I... I...

585
00:38:04,420 --> 00:38:06,220
I’m still having nightmares.

586
00:38:07,420 --> 00:38:08,780
Alright. Alright.

587
00:38:09,540 --> 00:38:10,620
It’s fine now.

588
00:38:12,180 --> 00:38:14,060
Your father thinks Li Wei’s wronged,

589
00:38:14,460 --> 00:38:15,820
but he cares more about you.

590
00:38:16,980 --> 00:38:18,380
So he agreed.

591
00:38:21,540 --> 00:38:22,580
I’ve sent people

592
00:38:22,580 --> 00:38:23,940
to wait outside the court.

593
00:38:24,340 --> 00:38:25,580
After the court is adjourned,

594
00:38:26,540 --> 00:38:28,220
they’ll get him here to comfort you.

595
00:38:30,260 --> 00:38:31,220
Mother,

596
00:38:32,260 --> 00:38:33,340
will father let Huaiji

597
00:38:33,340 --> 00:38:34,500
come back to me?

598
00:38:39,820 --> 00:38:40,700
Huirou,

599
00:38:43,020 --> 00:38:44,980
don’t mention this

600
00:38:44,980 --> 00:38:46,220
in front of your father again.

601
00:38:47,860 --> 00:38:48,620
Your father didn’t punish Huaiji,

602
00:38:48,620 --> 00:38:50,180
did he?

603
00:38:56,460 --> 00:38:57,260
But,

604
00:38:59,460 --> 00:39:01,020
I can’t live without Huaiji.

605
00:39:03,140 --> 00:39:03,980
Mother,

606
00:39:06,140 --> 00:39:07,940
Huaiji is like my shadow.

607
00:39:10,940 --> 00:39:11,820
Every person

608
00:39:13,940 --> 00:39:15,620
has a shadow.

609
00:39:18,580 --> 00:39:19,460
Unless

610
00:39:22,500 --> 00:39:24,700
it’s a ghost.

611
00:39:25,580 --> 00:39:27,340
Huirou, what are you talking about?

612
00:39:29,380 --> 00:39:32,980
I’m talking from my heart.

613
00:39:34,540 --> 00:39:36,100
Princess entered the palace at night.

614
00:39:36,180 --> 00:39:37,260
The gatekeepers opened the gate,

615
00:39:37,380 --> 00:39:39,220
they should be punished first.

616
00:39:39,220 --> 00:39:40,060
Enough!

617
00:39:45,500 --> 00:39:49,340
= Sima Guang, courtesy name Junshi =

618
00:39:51,060 --> 00:39:52,620
The gatekeepers failed in their duty.

619
00:39:53,340 --> 00:39:54,300
It’s true that they should be punished.

620
00:39:55,020 --> 00:39:56,260
But that’s not the point.

621
00:39:57,260 --> 00:39:58,580
Princess

622
00:39:58,580 --> 00:39:59,980
violated the palace prohibition

623
00:40:00,100 --> 00:40:01,540
and entered the palace at night.

624
00:40:02,420 --> 00:40:03,780
Why don’t you speak it loudly?

625
00:40:05,060 --> 00:40:06,140
He drew everyone’s attention

626
00:40:06,140 --> 00:40:07,140
to Princess?

627
00:40:08,140 --> 00:40:08,940
Sima Guang said

628
00:40:09,100 --> 00:40:11,060
Princess was unfilial to her mother-in-law

629
00:40:11,220 --> 00:40:12,340
and disrespected Prince Consort.

630
00:40:13,020 --> 00:40:14,780
Before entering the palace,

631
00:40:14,780 --> 00:40:16,100
Princess hurt Mrs. Yang.

632
00:40:16,700 --> 00:40:18,100
She didn’t feel guilty at all,

633
00:40:18,460 --> 00:40:20,860
and knocked on the palace gate at night,

634
00:40:21,420 --> 00:40:22,980
completely ignoring the palace prohibition

635
00:40:22,980 --> 00:40:23,860
and the safety of her father.

636
00:40:25,020 --> 00:40:26,340
Sima Guang also said

637
00:40:26,860 --> 00:40:27,900
Princess is a woman of loose morals,

638
00:40:28,340 --> 00:40:29,860
yet Li Wei always treated Princess modestly.

639
00:40:30,060 --> 00:40:30,900
He was not seriously at fault.

640
00:40:31,460 --> 00:40:32,740
Justice can’t be ignored.

641
00:40:32,820 --> 00:40:34,020
If the Emperor punishes Li Wei

642
00:40:34,220 --> 00:40:35,300
and protects Princess,

643
00:40:36,020 --> 00:40:37,540
it’d be unfair to Li Wei.

644
00:40:39,370 --> 00:40:40,880
If the Emperor is so biased,

645
00:40:41,410 --> 00:40:42,631
how can he be a model of the country?

646
00:40:42,860 --> 00:40:44,540
Sima Guang is so insolent.

647
00:40:44,580 --> 00:40:46,020
Why doesn’t His Majesty rebuke him?

648
00:40:46,620 --> 00:40:47,620
How can I rebuke him?

649
00:40:48,780 --> 00:40:49,900
What can I say?

650
00:40:51,980 --> 00:40:52,700
Your Majesty.

651
00:41:14,260 --> 00:41:16,020
Sima Guang was stating the truth.

652
00:41:16,820 --> 00:41:18,220
I couldn’t refute his accusation.

653
00:41:20,140 --> 00:41:21,460
Right after he finished his words,

654
00:41:21,460 --> 00:41:22,740
a censor said that

655
00:41:24,660 --> 00:41:27,100
some eunuchs didn’t behave themselves.

656
00:41:28,140 --> 00:41:29,980
Maybe it was these eunuchs that sowed discord

657
00:41:30,780 --> 00:41:32,540
between Princess and the Li family.

658
00:41:33,740 --> 00:41:34,620
They said

659
00:41:35,180 --> 00:41:37,500
all the eunuchs in Princess’s Mansion

660
00:41:38,780 --> 00:41:40,060
should be punished.

661
00:41:41,620 --> 00:41:44,380
Father, are you going to punish Huaiji?

662
00:41:45,660 --> 00:41:46,660
He was not at fault.

663
00:41:47,620 --> 00:41:48,860
He never pits me

664
00:41:48,860 --> 00:41:49,820
against Li Wei.

665
00:41:51,300 --> 00:41:52,300
I’m willing to

666
00:41:53,220 --> 00:41:54,460
take any punishment.

667
00:41:55,860 --> 00:41:57,660
Your father doesn’t want to punish you,

668
00:41:59,340 --> 00:42:00,180
or any eunuch

669
00:42:00,180 --> 00:42:01,340
from your mansion.

670
00:42:03,420 --> 00:42:05,300
However, the moment you entered the palace,

671
00:42:06,300 --> 00:42:08,500
you already exposed this family affair

672
00:42:08,980 --> 00:42:10,620
to the public.

673
00:42:13,700 --> 00:42:14,860
Because of this,

674
00:42:16,620 --> 00:42:17,900
Li Wei was also involved

675
00:42:19,740 --> 00:42:21,580
and was demoted.

676
00:42:22,260 --> 00:42:24,140
So you’ve actually interfered in court affairs.

677
00:42:25,340 --> 00:42:26,700
Now it’s even impossible for the censors

678
00:42:27,220 --> 00:42:28,340
to turn a blind eye to it.

679
00:42:30,060 --> 00:42:31,540
No matter it’s a family affair,

680
00:42:32,140 --> 00:42:33,540
or a state affair,

681
00:42:34,340 --> 00:42:35,700
Huaiji didn’t do anything wrong.

682
00:42:37,220 --> 00:42:38,660
He never pits me

683
00:42:38,660 --> 00:42:39,620
against Li Wei.

684
00:42:41,020 --> 00:42:42,300
I’m willing to

685
00:42:43,220 --> 00:42:44,540
take any punishment.

686
00:43:02,340 --> 00:43:09,300
♪ Memory is the breath of deep sleep ♪

687
00:43:09,860 --> 00:43:16,780
♪ It emerges in every crevice ♪

688
00:43:17,260 --> 00:43:23,620
♪ Shallow dreams are like
copper bells under eaves ♪

689
00:43:24,060 --> 00:43:30,820
♪ Woken up when the wind blows ♪

690
00:43:32,060 --> 00:43:38,860
♪ Fate is predetermined ♪

691
00:43:39,460 --> 00:43:46,180
♪ Struggle to break out of it ♪

692
00:43:46,740 --> 00:43:53,780
♪ Who will battle fate with me ♪

693
00:43:53,780 --> 00:44:00,620
♪ Regardless of the ending ♪

694
00:44:05,500 --> 00:44:09,020
♪ Peach branches shake in the spring breeze ♪

695
00:44:09,220 --> 00:44:12,820
♪ Walls sigh, the wind is silent ♪

696
00:44:12,820 --> 00:44:16,020
♪ The boy beside the wall is unaware of it ♪

697
00:44:16,020 --> 00:44:20,420
♪ He plays with the butterfly, gathering honey ♪

698
00:44:20,420 --> 00:44:24,140
♪ Peach blossoms tell a love story ♪

699
00:44:24,140 --> 00:44:27,700
♪ About a couple who lives happily ♪

700
00:44:27,700 --> 00:44:31,420
♪ Unluckily deep love comes to nowhere ♪

701
